OL,7,F"Jody was a strong beautiful girl
OL,8,Finside and out, a very loving mother,"
OL,9,Fsaid Linda Brough, Jody's mother.
OL,11,F"There's no words to describe her
OL,12,Freally, she was an exceptional loving
OL,13,Fgirl, always willing to help anybody.
OL,15,FJody's family are now calling for the
OL,16,FNHS to change its practice of only
OL,17,Foffering smear tests to people over
OL,18,Fthe age of 25.
