OL,7,FIt was only through privately paid for
OL,8,Ftests at Park Hill Hospital that
OL,9,FJody's worst fears were confirmed.
OL,11,F"They found stage two cervical
OL,12,Fcancer," said Linda. "It was already
OL,13,Fwell-established in there, if she'd
OL,14,Fbeen able to get there a couple of
OL,15,Fmonths earlier, it could have made all
OL,16,Fthe difference.J"Somebody needs to
OL,17,Ftake notice of what's happening to
OL,18,Fthese girls," she said.
OL,20,F"It's not fair what's happening."
