OL,7,FTo raise awareness of the issue and
OL,8,Ffundraise for the Amber's Legacy
OL,9,Fcharity - which supported Jody during
OL,10,Ftreatment and campaigns for smear
OL,11,Ftests at a younger age - Jody's friend
OL,12,FVicky Hogg will run from Edinburgh to
OL,13,FLondon, covering 36 miles a day while
OL,14,Fpulling her own supplies.
OL,16,F"I want to do her proud, and do her
OL,17,Ffamily proud, and raise as much money
OL,18,Fas possible," said Vicky.
