OL,7,F"It's so important for women to get
OL,8,Fthe smear, don't be embarrassed, don't
OL,9,Fput it off, just go and get it done
OL,10,Fit's so important."
OL,12,FDr Stuart Griffiths from Yorkshire
OL,13,FCancer Research agrees.
OL,15,F"With cervical cancer, if it's not
OL,16,Fspread, is very easy to treat," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
