OL,7,F"If we can find it as early as
OL,8,Fpossible, then the vast majority -
OL,9,Fover 95% - of people will survive, so
OL,10,Ffinding it early is critical."JWhile
OL,11,Fthat message is supported by the
OL,12,FDepartment of Health and Social Care,
OL,13,Fit says evidence shows screening under
OL,14,Fthe age of 25 does more harm than good
OL,15,Fand can lead to unnecessary medical
OL,16,Fprocedures.
OL,18,FJody's family, however, will keep
OL,19,Fcampaigning for change, in the hope
OL,20,Fthat it might make a difference to
OL,21,Fothers.
